\c 1
\s UMozisi ulandisa ngokwenzakalayo ekuhambeni kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli enkangala
\p
\v 1 La ngamazwi uMozisi awakhuluma kuIsrayeli wonke nganeno kweJordani enkangala, egcekeni eliqondene leSufi, phakathi kweParani leTofeli leLabani\x + 1 Sam. 25.1. Nani 10.12.\x* leHazerothi leDizahabi\x + Nani 11.35. 12.16. 33.17.\x*.
\v 2 Kulensuku ezilitshumi lanye kusukela eHorebe ngendlela yentaba yeSeyiri kusiya eKadeshi-Bhaneya\x + Nani 13.26. 32.8. 34.4. 2.14. 9.23.\x*.
\v 3 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wamatshumi amane, ngenyanga yetshumi lanye, ngolokuqala lwenyanga\x + Nani 33.38.\x*, uMozisi wakhuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamlaya ngakho kubo,
\v 4 esemtshayile uSihoni inkosi yamaAmori\x + Nani 21.24,26.\x* owayehlala eHeshiboni\x + Nani 21.24,26.\x*, loOgi inkosi yeBashani\x + Nani 21.33. Josh. 12.4. 13.12. 3.1,10.\x* owayehlala eAshitarothi eEdreyi.
\v 5 Nganeno kweJordani, elizweni lakoMowabi, uMozisi waqala ukuchasisa lumlayo esithi:
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yakhuluma kithi eHorebe isithi: Selihlale isikhathi eseneleyo kulintaba\x + Eks. 19.1. Nani 10.11; 2.3.\x*.
\v 7 Phendukani lisuke, liye entabeni yamaAmori, lendaweni ezakhelene lawo, egcekeni, entabeni, lesihotsheni, leningizimu, lekhunjini lolwandle, ilizwe lamaKhanani, leLebhanoni, kuze kube semfuleni omkhulu, umfula iYufrathi.
\v 8 Bonani, ngibeke ilizwe phambi kwenu. Ngenani, lidle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo, oAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe, ukubanika lona lenzalo yabo emva kwabo\x + Gen. 12.7. 15.18. 17.7,8. 26.4. 28.13. 50.24.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Njalo ngakhuluma kini ngalesosikhathi ngisithi: Kangilakulithwala ngingedwa\x + Num. 11.14. Eks. 18.18\x*.
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ilandisile\x + Gen. 15.5. Dute. 28.62.\x*, khangelani-ke, lamuhla linjengenkanyezi zamazulu ngobunengi.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, kayandise kini, njengoba linjalo, ngokuphindwe kankulungwane, ilibusise, njengokukhuluma kwayo kini\x + 2 Sam. 24.3.\x*.
\v 12 Ngingedwa ngingathwala njani\x + 1 Kho. 3.8,9.\x* ubunzima benu lomthwalo wenu lenkani yenu\x + Isa. 1.14.\x*?
\v 13 Zithatheleni amadoda ahlakaniphileyo, azwisisayo, laziwayo ezizweni zenu, ngiwabeke-ke abe zinhloko zenu\x + Eks. 18.21. Nani 11.16,17.\x*.
\v 14 Laselingiphendula lisithi: Ilizwi olikhulumileyo lilungile ukulenza.
\v 15 Ngasengithatha inhloko zezizwe zenu, amadoda ahlakaniphileyo, aziwayo, ngawabeka aba zinhloko phezu kwenu, induna zezinkulungwane, lenduna zamakhulu, lenduna zamatshumi amahlanu, lenduna zamatshumi\x + Eks. 18.25.\x*, leziphathamandla zezizwe zenu\x + Nani 11.16.\x*.
\v 16 Ngasengilaya abahluleli benu ngalesosikhathi ngisithi: Zwanini \add oku\add*phakathi kwabafowenu, lahlulele ngokulunga phakathi komuntu lomfowabo lowezizweni \add oku\add*ye\x + Joha. 7.24.\x*.
\v 17 Lingakhangeli ubuso ekwahluleleni, zwanini omncinyane njengomkhulu; lingesabi ubuso bomuntu\x + Levi 19.15.16.19. 1 Sam. 16.7. Zaga 24.23. Jak. 2.1,9.\x*, ngoba ukwahlulela kungokukaNkulunkulu. Lendaba elukhuni kini\x + 2 Lan. 19.6.\x* lizayiletha kimi, besengiyizwa\x + Eks. 18.22,26.\x*.
\v 18 Langalesosikhathi ngalilaya zonke izinto elifanele ukuzenza.
\p
\v 19 Sasesisuka eHorebe, sahamba kuyo yonke leyonkangala enkulu leyesabekayo elayibonayo ngendlela yentaba yamaAmori, njengokusilaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 8.15. Nani 10.12. Jer. 2.6.\x*, saze safika eKadeshi-Bhaneya\x + 1.2. 2.14.\x*.
\v 20 Ngasengisithi kini: Selifikile entabeni yamaAmori iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu ezasinika yona.
\v 21 Bona, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ilinikile ilizwe phambi kwakho; yenyuka udle ilifa lalo, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo kuwe; ungesabi, ungadideki\x + Josh. 1.9. Dute. 31.8.\x*.
\v 22 Laselisondela kimi lonke lathi: Asithume amadoda phambi kwethu ukuze asihlolele ilizwe, abuyise ilizwi kithi, indlela esizakwenyuka ngayo, lemizi esizangena kuyo.
\v 23 Lendaba yayinhle emehlweni ami; ngakho ngathatha kini amadoda alitshumi lambili, indodanye ngesizwe\x + Nani 13.3.\x*.
\v 24 Wona aphenduka, enyukela entabeni\x + Nani 13.22-27.\x* aze afika esihotsheni seEshikoli, asihlola.
\v 25 Asethatha okwezithelo zelizwe esandleni sabo, azehlisela kithi; abuyisa ilizwi kithi athi: Ilizwe lihle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu esinika lona.
\v 26 Kanti kalifunanga ukwenyuka, kodwa lavukela umlomo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 1.43. Josh. 1.18. Hlab. 107.11.\x*,
\v 27 langunguna emathenteni enu lathi\x + Hlab. 106.25. Nani 14.1-4.\x*: Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayisizonda, yasikhupha elizweni leGibhithe ukusinikela esandleni samaAmori ukusibhubhisa\x + 9.28.\x*.
\v 28 Sizakwenyukela ngaphi? Abafowethu benze inhliziyo yethu iphele amandla\x + Josh. 14.8.\x* besithi: Abantu bakhulu bade kulathi; imizi mikhulu, ibiyelwe ngemithangala efika emazulwini\x + Nani 13.28-33. Dute. 9.1,2.\x*; futhi-ke sibonile khona amadodana amaAnaki\x + Nani 13.22.\x*.
\v 29 Ngasengisithi kini: Lingatshaywa luvalo, libesabe.
\v 30 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ehamba phambi kwenu, yona izalilwela njengakho konke eyalenzela khona eGibhithe phambi kwamehlo enu\x + Eks. 14.14,25. Neh. 4.20.\x*,
\v 31 lenkangala, lapho obone khona ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakuthwala njengendoda ithwala indodana yayo, endleleni yonke elahamba ngayo laze lafika kulindawo\x + Eks. 19.4. 32.11,12. Isa. 46.3,4. 63.9. Hos. 11.3. Seb. 13.18.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa ngalelilizwi kalikholwanga iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Hlab. 106.24. Juda 5.\x*
\v 33 eyahamba phambi kwenu endleleni\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*, ukulidingela indawo ukuze limise inkamba, ngomlilo ebusuku, ukulitshengisa indlela elizahamba ngayo, langeyezi emini\x + Nani 10.33.\x*.
\v 34 Kwathi iN\nd kosi\nd* isizwile ilizwi lamazwi enu, yathukuthela yafunga yathi\x + 2.14,15.\x*:
\v 35 Isibili kakho kulamadoda alesisizukulwana esibi ozabona ilizwe elihle engafunga ukulinika oyihlo\x + Nani 14.22,23,29. Hlab. 95.11.\x*,
\v 36 ngaphandle kukaKalebi indodana kaJefune; yena uzalibona. Njalo ngizanika kuye ilizwe anyathela kulo, lakubantwana bakhe, ngoba ulandele iN\nd kosi\nd* ngokupheleleyo\x + Nani 14.24,30. Josh. 14.9.\x*.
\v 37 Lami iN\nd kosi\nd* yangithukuthelela ngenxa yenu, isithi: Lawe kawuyikungena khona\x + 4.21. Nani 20.12. 27.13,14.3.26. 32.51. 34.4. Hlab. 106.32.\x*.
\v 38 UJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + Nani 13.16.\x* oma phambi kwakho, yena uzangena khona\x + Eks. 24.13. 1 Sam. 16.22.\x*; mqinise, ngoba yena uzakwenza uIsrayeli adle ilifa lalo\x + Nani 27.18-20. Dute. 31.7,23.\x*.
\v 39 Labantwanyana benu elalisithi bazakuba yimpango, labantwana benu\x + Nani 14.3,31.\x*, abangaziyo lamuhla okuhle lokubi, bona bazangena khona; lakubo ngizalinika, bona-ke bazakudla ilifa lalo\x + Isa. 7.15,16.\x*.
\v 40 Kodwa lina ziphendukeleni, lisuke liye enkangala, indlela yoLwandle oluBomvu\x + Nani 14.25; Dute. 2.1.\x*.
\v 41 Laseliphendula lisithi kimi: Sonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; thina sizakwenyuka siyekulwa, njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu eyasilaya khona\x + Nani 14.40.\x*. Selihlomile, ngulowo lalowo isikhali sakhe sempi, lacabanga ukuthi kulula ukwenyukela entabeni.
\v 42 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Tshono kubo: Lingenyuki, lingalwi, ngoba kangikho phakathi kwenu, hlezi litshaywe phambi kwezitha zenu\x + Nani 14.42.\x*.
\v 43 Ngasengikhuluma kini, kodwa kalilalelanga, lavukela umlomo weN\nd kosi\x + 1.26.\x*\nd*, laqholoza lenyukela entabeni.
\v 44 Kwathi amaAmori ayehlala entabeni leyo aphuma ukumelana lani, alixotsha\x + Nani 14.45.\x* njengokwenziwa zinyosi, alihlakaza eSeyiri, kwaze kwaba seHorma\x + Hlab. 118.12.\x*.
\v 45 Laselibuya, lakhala inyembezi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kayilizwanga ilizwi lenu, kayibekanga indlebe kini.
\v 46 Laselihlala eKadeshi insuku ezinengi, njengensuku elahlala ngazo\x + Nani 20.1,22. Hlu. 11.17.\x*.
